title: E3 annual video game showcase event in Los Angeles cancelled
description: It had been due to return as an in-person event in Los Angeles for the first time in four years in June.

title: York student uses AI chatbot to get parking fine revoked
description: The 22-year-old turned to a chatbot to give her a "professional" letter to appeal her parking fine.

title: Google faces new multi-billion advertising lawsuit
description: The case seeks £3.4bn in compensation for publishers from the search giant.

title: US-China chip war: Japan plans to restrict some equipment exports
description: The measures, which are planned to take effect in July, follow similar moves by the US and the Netherlands.
